prompt.title: Embedding for Promptbook: Defining AI Workflow Components
prompt.content: Promptbook consists of three main components: "What" (Workflows, Tasks, and Parameters), "Who" (Personas), and "How" (Knowledge, Instruments, and Actions). These components define the work to be done, who performs it, and the resources used, respectively.
